text: USS Honolulu has been the name of more than one United States Navy ship, and may refer to: *USS Honolulu (ID-1843), a cargo ship in commission from 1917 to 1919 *, a light cruiser in commission from 1938 from 1947 *, a submarine in commission from 1985 to 2007 Category:United States Navy ship names
title: USS Honolulu
